about.summary: Calculate generalized R-squared, partial R-squared, and partial correlation coefficients for generalized linear models (including quasi models with well defined variance functions).

name: r-rsq
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set version = '1.1' %}
{% set posix = 'm2-' if win else '' %}
{% set native = 'm2w64-' if win else '' %}

package:
  name: r-rsq
  version: {{ version|replace("-", "_") }}

source:
  url:
    - {{ cran_mirror }}/src/contrib/rsq_{{ version }}.tar.gz
    - {{ cran_mirror }}/src/contrib/Archive/rsq/rsq_{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: 4e12584d2413a81095fa25c3c9a0da61666a6b1b3ebc6a428bcbcb7290f3765f

build:
  merge_build_host: True  # [win]
  number: 1
  noarch: generic
  rpaths:
    - lib/R/lib/
    - lib/

requirements:
  build:
    - {{posix}}zip               # [win]
  host:
    - r-base
    - r-mass
  run:
    - r-base
    - r-mass

test:
  commands:
    - $R -e "library('rsq')"           # [not win]
    - "\"%R%\" -e \"library('rsq')\""  # [win]

about:
  home: https://CRAN.R-project.org/package=rsq
  license: GPL-2
  summary: Calculate generalized R-squared, partial R-squared, and partial correlation coefficients
    for generalized linear models (including quasi models with well defined variance
    functions).
  license_family: GPL2
  license_file: '{{ environ["PREFIX"] }}/lib/R/share/licenses/GPL-2'

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - conda-forge/r
    - PertuyF
